AMASSET.ARLLESSORID, AMASSET.ARSTRLICCNTRID, AMASSET.ARLLICCNTRID, AMASSET.ARSTRMAINTCNTRID, AMASSET.ARLMAINTCNTRID, AMASSET.ARSTRMODELID, AMASSET.ARLMODELID, AMASSET.ARSTRPORDLINEID, AMASSET.ARLSEVERITYID, AMASSET.ARSTRSUPPID, AMASSET.ARLSUPPID, AMASSET.ARSTRPFZFIXEDASTNOID, AMASSET.ARLPFZFIXEDASTNOID, AMASSET.ARSTRPFZASSIGNGROUPID, AMASSET.ARLPFZASSIGNGROUPID, AMASSET.PFZAGNAME, AMASSET.SERIALNO IS NULL THEN '' WHEN ((B.NAME ='LENOVO' OR B.NAME='IBM') AND LENGTH(TRIM(AMASSET.SERIALNO))=14) THEN SUBSTR(TRIM((REPLACE(REPLACE(AMASSET.SERIALNO,'-'),' '))), -7, 7) ELSE REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(AMASSET.SERIALNO,'-'),' '),'?'),'/') END AS SHORT_SN, CASE WHEN M.NAME IS NULL THEN '' WHEN M.NAME LIKE '%NETVISTA%' THEN 'NETVISTA' WHEN ((INSTR(M.NAME, '(')=0) AND (M.NAME NOT LIKE '%NETVISTA%')) THEN TRIM(REPLACE(M.NAME,'TABLET')) WHEN ((INSTR(M.NAME, '(')=1) AND (M.NAME NOT LIKE '%NETVISTA%')) THEN TRIM(REPLACE(SUBSTR(M.NAME,INSTR(M.NAME,'(')+1,INSTR(M.NAME,')')-2),'TABLET')) WHEN ((INSTR(M.NAME, '(')>1) AND (M.NAME NOT LIKE '%NETVISTA%')) THEN TRIM(REPLACE(SUBSTR(M.NAME,1,INSTR(M.NAME,'(')-1),'TABLET')) ELSE TRIM(M.NAME) END AS MODEL_TYPE FROM AMASSET, AMMODEL M, AMMODEL ST, AMMODEL T, AMBRAND B WHERE AMASSET.LMODELID = M.LMODELID (+) AND M.LPARENTID = ST.LMODELID (+) AND ST.LPARENTID = T.LMODELID (+) AND M.LBRANDID = B.LBRANDID (+)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select distinct rsys.netbios_name0, rsys.resourceid, rsys.ad_site_name0, rsys.Resource_domain_or_workgr0, cs.caption0, cs.version0, ws.lasthwscan, scu1.TopConsoleUser0, scu1.SecurityLogStartDate0, scu2.SystemConsoleUser0, scu2.LastConsoleUse0, NumberOfConsoleLogons0, TotalUserConsoleMinutes0, senc.Manufacturer0, senc.SerialNumber0, senc.ChassisTypes0, senc.SMBIOSAssetTag0, csp.name0, csp.version0, CASE When (rsys.resourceid in (select distinct resourceid from v_clientcollectionmembers where collectionid in (select collectionid from v_collection where name = 'All Office Client Systems'))) then 'OFFICE' When (rsys.resourceid in (select distinct resourceid from v_clientcollectionmembers where collectionid in (select collectionid from v_collection where name = 'All Automation Systems'))) then 'AUTOMATION' When (rsys.resourceid in (select distinct resourceid from v_clientcollectionmembers where collectionid in (select collectionid from v_collection where name = 'All Benchtop Systems'))) then 'BENCHTOP' When (rsys.resourceid in (select distinct resourceid from v_clientcollectionmembers where collectionid in (select collectionid from v_collection where name = 'All Kiosk Systems'))) then 'KIOSK' When (rsys.resourceid in (select distinct resourceid from v_clientcollectionmembers where collectionid in (select collectionid from v_collection where name = 'All Tablet Client Systems'))) then 'TABLET' END as 'USE' from v_r_system_valid rsys join v_gs_workstation_status ws on ws.resourceid = rsys.resourceid join v_gs_operating_system cs on cs.resourceid = rsys.resourceid join v_gs_system_console_usage scu1 on scu1.resourceid = rsys.resourceid join v_gs_system_console_user scu2 on scu2.resourceid = rsys.resourceid join v_GS_SYSTEM_ENCLOSURE senc on senc.resourceid = rsys.resourceid join v_GS_COMPUTER_SYSTEM_PRODUCT csp on csp.resourceid = rsys.resourceid order by rsys.netbios_name0
